                   pricePercent SHOWIF isPricePercent(o) ON CHANGE changePricePercent(pd), 
                   calcPriceCoeff SHOWIF isPriceCoeff(o) ON CHANGE changePriceCoeff(pd),                   
                   price ON CHANGE changeProductsPrice(pd), sum
